<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الخَمِيس:</span> يُجْمَعُ في أدْنى العَدَدِ على <span class="c1">"أَخْمِسَة"</span> كـ <span class="c1">"قَفِيز وأَقْفِزَة"</span> وتجمع على <span class="c1">"أَخْمَاس"</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وجَمع الكَثرةِ <span class="c1">"الخُمُس"</span> و <span class="c1">"الخُمْسَان"</span> وعلى <span class="c1">"أخْمِسَاء"</span> كنصيب وأَنْصِبَاء.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>